title: Dakine Sean Pettit Team Heli Pro 20L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Sean Pettit Team Heli Pro 20L.

- Vertical snowboard carry
- Diagonal ski carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Laptop sleeve
